HEADWORD: Omophagic
<hw>O"mo*phag"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'wmofa`gos</grk>; <grk>'wmo`s</grk> raw + <grk>fagei^n</grk> to
